description.en:
What is the project about?
yukky is a meme project

What makes your project unique?
Unlike other meme tokens, we are a safe meme project that received code audit and kyc from teach rate.
https://twitter.com/TechAudit1/status/1657278638893531136

History of your project.
We started pre-funding on May 13, 2023 and launched on uniswap on May 20.

What’s next for your project?
We are currently discussing the plan to list on cex after confirming the listing on top25cex and listing on 5 additional exchanges.

What can your token be used for?
We plan to develop as a meme coin by listing on many cex and making it a large community.
